title: Patreon
body:
I know a few people on here have inquired on wether I have a Patreon or not anymore, and I’ve decided to relaunch, but solely as a tip jar. 

If you are interested, you can pledge or follow at patreon.com/swollenbabyfat! Everything will be public, and I plan to keep on sharing everything for free. Hopefully in the future I can have physical merch teirs, but that will be some time in the future.
